profile:
Silkwood Lawn & Garden is Kingston's all in one maintenance company!  We specialize in sprinkler (irrigation) systems; lawn maintenance including plug air-ration, over-seeding, fertilizing, lawn cutting; snow plowing, fences and property management.
Contact us at:
613-384-6440
info@silkwoodlawnandgarden.com
www.silkwoodlawnandgarden.com
